YAYA (Yet Another Yara Automaton)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LOKI & THOR(Lite)       Available on Linux & Windows
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Loki already has a set of Yara rules
            1- cd loki
            2- python loki.py -h                <-to see what options are available
            3- python loki.py --update          <-will update signature-base directory, which Loki uses to scan for known evil. 
            4- cd signature-base                <- contains drs:  iocs  miscs  yara
            5- ./loki.py -p .                   <- (-p) followed what path to scan 
